    "• AR Evaluation: We evaluate AR using three main types of white-box attacks: PGD (with two different iteration steps P GD 10 and P GD 20), the C&W attack, and Auto-Attack.",
    "• Generalization Evaluation: We report generalization performance by generalization error under both AR (GE AR) and PR settings (GE PR D (γ)).",
    "A.4 MODEL AND DATASET SELECTION (2) it includes an extensive evaluation of widely used models and datasets, covering representative training methods designed for both AR and PR, enabling direct comparisons under PR metrics and revealing the performance of these methods in both adversarial and probabilistic scenarios; and (3) it presents in-depth analyses of the generalization error for PR from empirical and theoretical perspectives, which, to the best of our knowledge, has not been explored in prior benchmarks.",
